   2-SDA  --> SSD1306 & AT24C256 (EEPROM)
   3-SCL  --> SSD1306 & AT24C256 (EEPROM)
   4      --> S1 Analog Multiplexer 2
   5      --> S2 Analog Multiplexer 2
   6      --> S3 Analog Multiplexer 2
   7      --> ButtonPad Led GND 1
   8      --> ButtonPad Led GND 2
   9      --> ButtonPad Led GND 3
   10     --> ButtonPad Led GND 4 
   14     --> S2  Analog Multiplexer 1
   15     --> S1  Analog Multiplexer 1
   16     --> S3  Analog Multiplexer 1
   A0     --> SIG Analog Multiplexer 1 (input/input_pullup/analog)
   A1     --> S0  Analog Multiplexer 1
   A2     --> SIG Analog Multiplexer 2 (output/analog_input)
   A3     --> S0  Analog Multiplexer 2
__________________________________________________________________________________________
*******************      Analog 16 channel Analog Multiplexer (1)      *******************
   00      --> ButtonPad SWITCH 1
   01      --> ButtonPad SWITCH 2
   02      --> ButtonPad SWITCH 3
   03      --> ButtonPad SWITCH 4
   04      --> Potentiometer
   05      --> N/A
   06      --> N/A
   07      --> N/A
   08      --> Rotary Encoder1 Button
   09      --> Rotary Encoder1 pin1 DT
   10      --> Rotary Encoder1 pin2 CLK
   11      --> N/A
   12      --> N/A
   13      --> N/A
   14      --> N/A
   15      --> N/A
__________________________________________________________________________________________
*******************      Analog 16 channel Analog Multiplexer (2)      *******************
   00      --> ButtonPad Led RED   1
   01      --> ButtonPad Led BLUE  1
   02      --> ButtonPad Led GREEN 1
   03      --> ButtonPad Led RED   2
   04      --> ButtonPad Led BLUE  2
   05      --> ButtonPad Led GREEN 2
   06      --> ButtonPad Led RED   3
   07      --> ButtonPad Led BLUE  3
   08      --> ButtonPad Led GREEN 3
   09      --> ButtonPad Led RED   4
   10      --> ButtonPad Led BLUE  4
   11      --> ButtonPad Led GREEN 4
   12      --> ButtonPad SWITCH GND 1 with 2.2kohm resistor to 5v
   13      --> ButtonPad SWITCH GND 2 with 2.2kohm resistor to 5v
   14      --> ButtonPad SWITCH GND 3 with 2.2kohm resistor to 5v
